subduction\" prevails, giving way to modern style plate tectonics as both the\nmantle interior and climate cool. Hadean proto-subduction may hasten the onset\nof modern plate tectonics by drawing excess CO$_2$ out of the atmosphere and\ncooling the climate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Oct 2014 17:46:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
