tely spanned by a\nconical intersection seam.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Oct 2014 03:08:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Jan 2015 23:15:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-04"}
