amics and its implications\naround rotating BHs in the Newtonian framework, avoiding GR gas dynamical\nequations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Oct 2014 08:36:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-11"}
